    "Each entity in GCMD+ is assigned with a unique hierarchical path and identifier, resulting in a total of 16,360 entities, an 18% increase over the base GCMD.",
    "To enhance interoperability, we link the taxonomy to a cross-domain knowledge base, Wikidata, through Entity Matching and Metadata Integration, detailed in Appendix A.1.",
    "Why Not General Taxonomies?",
    "Broad resources like Wikidata introduce noise through excessive granularity (e.g., redundant storm classifications by years) and irrelevant entities.",
    "Domainspecific taxonomies prioritize precision, leveraging curated hierarchies validated by practitioners."
